snippet.title: Exodus Gods and Kings Official Trailer + Trailer Review : Beyond The Trailer

localized.description:
Exodus Gods and Kings debuts its official trailer for 2014, starring Christian Bale!  Watch it today with a trailer review!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Exodus Gods and Kings debuts its official trailer for 2014 and you can see it here today plus get a trailer review!  Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph gives you her reaction to this trailer for Exodus Gods and Kings starring Christian Bale, Joel Edgerton and Sigourney Weaver, directed by Ridley Scott!  Is this movie whitewashed?!  And with Beyond The Trailer's Trailer Plus, you'll get a link to other movie news, reviews, and trailers!  Enjoy this official HD trailer and trailer review for Exodus Gods and Kings before you see the full movie in 2014!  And make Beyond The Trailer your first stop for entertainment news on YouTube today!
